title: Build some nesting boxes

pars: This spring, with the near perfect conditions, birds are breeding prolifically. Nesting boxes encourage local bird life, especially in areas where there are a limited number of hollows for birds such as rosellas and galahs.
This adult male Eastern Rosella has just fed one of its young in a back yard nesting box in Rushworth, providing much joy to the property owner.
